                    <p>STEP 1 - Enter your query proteome:</p>
                  </div>
       <form name="sanspanz" id="sanspanz" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post" action="http://ekhidna2.biocenter.helsinki.fi/cgi-bin/sans/dump_AAI.cgi" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;" target="_blank">
        <input type="hidden" name="method" value="AAI">
        <input type="hidden" name="maxquery" value=100000>
                  <p>Paste proteome in FASTA format (<A HREF=./examples/thylacine/input.fasta target=_blank>example</A>, text area limited to 10M characters):</p> <textarea name="query" maxlength="10000000"
 rows="8" cols="60"></textarea> <br>
		  <p>or upload a proteome FASTA file: <INPUT TYPE="file" NAME="file">  
<!-- whet 1.12 installed; wget < 1.18 are vulnerable to hacking-->
		  <p>or load proteome FASTA file from URL: <INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="upload_URL" SIZE=60 > (restricted to NCBI genome or EBI database ftp servers)

                  <p>or paste the checksum of a recent job: <INPUT TYPE="text" size=40 NAME="hid"></p>

	           <div id="info">
                    <p>STEP 2 - Optional inputs:</p>
                  </div>
