       	<H2>Genome sequencing projects that used AAI-profiler:</H2>
	<H4>Archaea</H4>
        -<i>Halobellus captivus</i> sp. nov. (<A HREF=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs10482-019-01332-1>publication</A>)<br>
	-<i>Halorubrum amylolyticum</i> sp. nov. (<A HREF=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10482-019-01313-4>publication</A>)<br>
        -<i>Haloterrigena salifodinae </i> sp. nov. (<A HREF=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs10482-019-01264-w>publication</A>)<br>
  	<H4>Bacteria</H4>
        -<i>Alcaligenaceae</i> sp. Strain 429 (<A HREF=https://mra.asm.org/content/ga/8/19/e00439-19.full.pdf>publication</A>)<br>
	-<i>Deferribacter autotrophicus</i> (<A HREF=https://www.mdpi.com/2073-4425/10/11/849/htm>publication</A>)<br>
	-<i>Schlegelella brevitalea</i> sp. nov. (<A HREF=https://ijs.microbiologyresearch.org/content/journal/ijsem/10.1099/ijsem.0.003571>publication</A>)<br>
	-<i>Vibrio chemaguriensis</i> sp. nov. (<A HREF=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00284-019-01731-7>publication</A>)<br>
	<H4>Metagenome assembled genomes</H4>
	-Dinosaur bone (<A HREF=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1186/s40793-020-00355-w>publication</A>)<br>

